# Appreciations

A simple API to interact with the appreciations for C2.

## Apprecaitions Collection [/v1/appreciations/{?offset,limit}]



### Get a list of all Appreciations [GET]

Gives a JSON array containing a list of the appreciations. 


+ Parameters
    + offset (number) - The offset; Eg: 0 would be the first offset
    + limit (number) - The number of apprecations requested; Eg: 50


+ Response 200 (application/json)

