### Save an appreciation [POST]

Takes a JSON object containing a text string as the appreciations
and a array of users who the appreciation refers to.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "text": "Thanks for saving my life and the city of New York once again!",
            "author": "April O'Neil",
            "category":"general",
            "usersTagged": [
                                {
                                    "name": "Leonardo",
                                    "id": "3001"
                                }, {
                                    "name": "Donatello",
                                    "id": "3002"
                                }, {
                                    "name": "Michelangelo",
                                    "id": "3003"
                                }, {
                                    "name": "Raphael",
                                    "id": "3004"
                                }
                            ]
        }

