## Apprecaition [/v1/appreciation/{appreciation_id}]

+ Parameters
    + appreciation_id (number) - ID of the appreciation in the form of an integer

### Get an appreciation [GET]

Gives a JSON object containing an appreciation for the requested id. 

+ Response 200 (application/json)

